steps.name: Open Mit Id testing tool Link
Click upper left side search box and type CPR number which you want to login
Click on search box and copy create identity
Switch new tab and open shopper link and paste create identity click on continue
Switch to Mit Id tab and scroll to Open simulator and click it
Switch to open simulator and click on conform it
Switch to Mit Id and copy CPR number
Switch shopper tab paste CPR number and click continue
